cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM 

The paper deals with human pose estimation, which is a subfield of computer vision. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also introduces a new architecture and learning technique, which involves deep learning and neural networks, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) likely sub-categories as well. The paper also discusses the use of weak spatial models, which could fall under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) or cs.MM (Multimedia).
